# 🎯 AI Mock Interview Platform

An AI-powered full-stack mock interview platform that helps users prepare for technical, HR, and system design interviews using intelligent AI-based answer evaluation, speech analysis, and real-time feedback.

---

## 🌟 Overview

The AI Mock Interview Platform simulates real interview scenarios where users can practice answering questions, receive AI-generated evaluations, and improve communication, grammar, fluency, and confidence.

The platform supports:

- HR Interview Preparation
- Technical Interview Practice
- System Design Interviews
- Text & Voice Responses
- AI-Driven Answer Assessment

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🎤 Interview Experience
✅ Text-Based Interview Questions  
✅ Voice Answer Support (Speech-to-Text)  
✅ Multiple Interview Categories  
✅ Real-Time Interview Simulation  

### 🤖 AI Evaluation Engine
✅ AI-Powered Answer Evaluation  
✅ Grammar Analysis  
✅ Fluency Scoring  
✅ Confidence Assessment  
✅ Keyword Matching & Relevance Check  

### 📊 User Experience
✅ User Authentication (Signup/Login)  
✅ Interview Question Database  
✅ Professional Dashboard UI  
✅ Progress & Performance Tracking  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### AI Engine
- Python
- Flask
- spaCy
- NLP Processing

### Database
- MySQL (Railway Cloud Database)

### Deployment
- Backend → Render
- AI Engine → Render
- Database → Railway
- Frontend → Vercel

---

## 🏗 System Architecture

```txt
            Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)
                     │
                     ▼
        Node.js + Express Backend API
                     │
                     ▼
          Flask AI Evaluation Engine
                     │
                     ▼
            MySQL Cloud Database
```

