## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/MehakGupta1725/mock-interview-ai.git
cd mock-interview-ai
```

---

### 2️⃣ Setup Backend

Navigate to backend:

```bash
cd backend
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Start backend:

```bash
node server.js
```

---

### 3️⃣ Setup AI Engine

Navigate to AI Engine:

```bash
cd ai-engine
```

Install requirements:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run Flask server:

```bash
python app.py
```

---

### 4️⃣ Setup Database

Create MySQL database:

```sql
CREATE DATABASE mock_interview_db;
```

Create required tables:

- users
- questions

Configure environment variables.

---

### 5️⃣ Launch Frontend

Open:

```txt
frontend/index.html
```

or use **VS Code Live Server**.

---

## 🔐 Environment Variables

Backend `.env`

```env
MYSQLHOST=
MYSQLPORT=
MYSQLUSER=
MYSQLPASSWORD=
MYSQLDATABASE=
```

